  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  HIV infected

          -  KS of the oral cavity, pharynx and larynx, histopathologically confirmed

          -  HIV treatment-naïve

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Airway obstructive lesions

          -  Actively bleeding lesions

          -  Tumor-associated oedema or ulceration

          -  Gastrointestinal KS

          -  KS in other nonnodal viscera
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
